x; line-height: 30px; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0;">On Sunday, I=E2=80=
=99m hoping to have a look at another storied art dealer, whose collection =
will be auctioned in Switzerland this September. The works don=E2=80=99t lo=
ok cheap by any means, but after the recent bout of inflation, they might b=
e priced for today=E2=80=99s market. At least, there should be a lot of peo=
ple watching to get a better sense of the Modern market when works by <b>Ki=
rchner</b>, <b>Klee</b>, <b>Giacometti</b>, and other names all go up for s=
ale. <br/><br/>Until then,<br/>Marion<br/></td>
